item.title: Pickax Revolution Jeff Dornik on the Future of Social Media
item.description:
Join Yossi Schmidt as he sits down with Jeff Dornik, CEO of Pickax, to discuss the exciting new platform that's shaking up the social media landscape. Get an inside look at what's next for online connection and community building!
